WEBVTT

00:00:00.396 --> 00:00:03.696 A:middle
&gt;&gt; To complete your coding
assignments using the GitHub

00:00:03.696 --> 00:00:06.746 A:middle
Codespaces platform in
MindTap, you will have

00:00:06.746 --> 00:00:09.886 A:middle
to authorize GitHub to
access your MindTap course.

00:00:10.816 --> 00:00:13.606 A:middle
Note, you will only
have to do this once

00:00:13.656 --> 00:00:15.856 A:middle
when you launch the first
Coding Lab assignment

00:00:15.856 --> 00:00:17.816 A:middle
at the beginning
of your semester.

00:00:18.936 --> 00:00:21.766 A:middle
In order to complete this
authorization process,

00:00:22.186 --> 00:00:24.196 A:middle
you will need to have
a GitHub account.

00:00:25.186 --> 00:00:29.116 A:middle
You can use your existing
GitHub account or go

00:00:29.116 --> 00:00:31.716 A:middle
to github.com to
sign up for one.

00:00:33.076 --> 00:00:36.096 A:middle
As you launch your first
coding assignment in MindTap,

00:00:36.636 --> 00:00:38.696 A:middle
the authorization
screen will pop up.

00:00:39.756 --> 00:00:42.796 A:middle
Select the green button to
link your GitHub account

00:00:42.906 --> 00:00:44.246 A:middle
with your MindTap course.

00:00:45.276 --> 00:00:47.156 A:middle
Your account is now authorized

00:00:47.556 --> 00:00:49.556 A:middle
and you can begin
your assignments.

